09b29e98312b671e1eb2a8c22","tid":984532,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:32:37.000Z","msg":"神雞之墓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n神雞之墓埋葬著一隻「落都紅」種的母雞，根據碑誌記載，這隻母雞色紅艷美，體重3公斤、日產1卵，砲戰一開始，每逢對岸砲擊前約30分鐘，牠就展翅鳴啼，在營區內奔走示警，且屢試不爽，使得官兵能適時躲避、保全性命，因此被稱為「神雞」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2006/02/602260712071465-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2006%2F02%2F602260712071465-600x400.jpg&h=8a0946d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0488bbffab68557c151da85302a97d649969fec","tid":984532,"uid":170249,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"台灣當港澳已經係支那既一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日幫台狗講好說話既人情何以堪<br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立後一定成為av大國 加油台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25031de9c379135017b0db0e29182374cb4534f4","tid":984532,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"除非對歷史有興趣既人會去之外，我諗唔到理由外國人點解會選擇去呢個島玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8498e616804edc4e112faf36dc8a158193d43a","tid":984532,"uid":33028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cf82611ca1131a80050c6c5b788179fcd3ec1b1e","tid":984532,"uid":9681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"BNO?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:19:47.000Z","msg":"BNO都係要入台證,佢都係當你香港人"},{"pid":"e8b248cecbed2d6c11b7207e2769ed5a639ca7e8","tid":984532,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"幾撚醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/do